Name: TANKNAROK
About the game: TANKNAROK is a high speed, frenzied blastathon where 2-4 tanks go head to head in a wide range of arenas; filled to the brim with huge guns, powerful explosions and dangerous hazards! Wholesome roughhousing with either your friends at home, or friendly strangers on the internet! Key Features 2 to 4 players, either local or online! Play vs bots, alone or with friends! 90+ dangerous arenas across 7 different themes! Loads of power-ups, including awesome super weapons! Crunchy, crispy and juicy visual effects! Variation through 8 explosive game modes! Customize matches to your preferences!
